== 季度总结 ==
1946年大西洋飓风季于6月16日正式开始<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Season Officially Open But Weather Bureau Set For Winds | author = Wilbur Jennings | date = 1946-06-16 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The Palm Beach Post | page = 2 | location = Miami, Florida}}</ref>，但[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]早在三天前（6月13日）就开始出现热带天气活动。全季共形成七场热带风暴，略低于之前20年平均每季8.5场的水平<ref name="mwr">{{cite web | first = H.C. | last = Sumner | title = North Atlantic Hurricanes and Tropical Disturbances of 1946 | date = 1946-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224308/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1946.pdf | work = Monthly Weather Review | publisher = National Hurricane Center Library | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1946.pdf | accessdate = 2017-01-04 }}</ref>。共有三场风暴增强成飓风，但都没能强化成[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，即都达不到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的三级飓风标准，这在[[1940年大西洋飓风季|1940年]]后尚属首次，下一次重现则要到[[1968年大西洋飓风季|1968年]]<ref name="ACE" />。有一场飓风[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国，另外两场风暴在海上达到最高强度，风速至少为每小时119公里<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。所有气旋在美国引起的破坏数额不足1000万美元，而且没有人员遇难。风暴造成的损失至少有520万美元，<ref name="mwr" />其中最后一个气旋于11月3日消散<ref name="HURDAT" />，离飓风季于11月15日正式结束还有12天<ref>{{cite news | via = Newspapers.com | page = 10 | date = 1946-11-15 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/4786952/the_courier_news/ | title = Truman Seeks Seclusion on Florida Trip | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = Courier News | accessdate = 2017-01-04 | location = Key West, Florida | archive-date = 2019-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190606133239/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/4786952/the_courier_news/ | dead-url = no }} {{open access}}</ref>。

6月13日，[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]上空发展出热带风暴，提前拉开飓风季序幕。7月5日，第二场风暴在[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]近海成型。接下来大西洋盆地进入持续近七周的沉寂，直到8月25日才有第三个气旋在[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]形成。从气候角度而言，大西洋飓风季通常以九月最活跃，但这年九月却只有一个气旋达到热带风暴强度。全季最强风暴于9月12日成型，之后达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时155公里、最低[[气压|气压]]975[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.8[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。此外，[[中美洲|中美洲]]近海还曾短暂存在热带低气压。十月是本季最活跃的月份，共形成三个热带气旋，其中第三个便是全季最后一场风暴，最终持续到11月3日。<ref name="HURDAT" />

这年飓风季低迷的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值仅20，是[[1925年大西洋飓风季|1925年]]后新低，直到[[1983年大西洋飓风季|1983年]]才有更低的数值（17）出现<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | work = Hurricane Research Division; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-04 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425073956/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-12-24 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-04-25 }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高<ref name="Levinson">{{cite report |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-04-01 |location=Asheville, North Carolina |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>。

